{"data": [{"id": "4747489", "title": "NVDX: Key Nvidia Volatility Catalysts To Begin 2025, Wait For A Pullback", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412721464/image_1412721464.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Nvidia Corporation building in Taipei, Taiwan.\" data-id=\"1412721464\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412721464/image_1412721464.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412721464/image_1412721464.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412721464/image_1412721464.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412721464/image_1412721464.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412721464/image_1412721464.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412721464/image_1412721464.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412721464/image_1412721464.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412721464/image_1412721464.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">BING-JHEN HONG</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Nvidia Corporation</b><span> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVDA\" title=\"NVIDIA Corporation\">NVDA</a>) has turned choppy in the past six months. Since mid-July of 2024, the megacap tech stalwart has merely traded sideways, returning 1.4% since peaking ahead of the Q2 earnings season last summer. It has lost modest ground</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412721464/image_1412721464.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747489-nvdx-key-nvidia-volatility-catalysts-to-begin-2025-wait-for-a-pullback", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 18:45:28", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747485", "title": "Entegris: Well-Positioned, But Still Pricey", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075787099/image_2075787099.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Robotic arm giving a CPU to another robot\" data-id=\"2075787099\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1008px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075787099/image_2075787099.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075787099/image_2075787099.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075787099/image_2075787099.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075787099/image_2075787099.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075787099/image_2075787099.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075787099/image_2075787099.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075787099/image_2075787099.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075787099/image_2075787099.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">luza studios</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In the summer, I called shares of <strong>Entegris (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ENTG\" title=\"Entegris, Inc.\">ENTG</a></span>)</strong> expensive, despite anticipated improvements. In the half year which followed, shares have lost about a quarter of their value, as anticipated improvements in the second half of 2024 came in slower than</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075787099/image_2075787099.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747485-entegris-well-positioned-but-still-pricey", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 18:36:07", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747484", "title": "Kohl's: A Mismanaged Retailer Likely To Continue Falling", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163700120/image_2163700120.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Kohls Store\" data-id=\"2163700120\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163700120/image_2163700120.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163700120/image_2163700120.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163700120/image_2163700120.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163700120/image_2163700120.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163700120/image_2163700120.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163700120/image_2163700120.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163700120/image_2163700120.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163700120/image_2163700120.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">patty_c/iStock Unreleased via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Beleaguered retailer, <strong>Kohl\u2019s</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KSS\" title=\"Kohl's Corporation\">KSS</a></span>) continues to plummet amid heavy short interest on the stock. That looks totally warranted in my view, as Kohl\u2019s has an untenable amount of debt, stubbornly pays a dividend it cannot</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163700120/image_2163700120.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747484-kohls-mismanaged-retailer-likely-to-continue-falling", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 18:34:29", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747014", "title": "First Internet Bancorp: Floating Debt Securities Offer High Single-Digit Yield", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185938635/image_2185938635.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"woman sit in front restaurant and shop online with credit card\" data-id=\"2185938635\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185938635/image_2185938635.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185938635/image_2185938635.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185938635/image_2185938635.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185938635/image_2185938635.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185938635/image_2185938635.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185938635/image_2185938635.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185938635/image_2185938635.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185938635/image_2185938635.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Miljan \u017divkovi\u0107/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Introduction</strong></h2> <p>Although I\u2019m currently not a shareholder of First Internet Bancorp (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INBK\" title=\"First Internet Bancorp\">INBK</a></span>) I'm keeping an eye on its financial results as I still <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4701988-first-internet-bancorp-bottoming-net-interest-margin-bodes-well-future\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4701988-first-internet-bancorp-bottoming-net-interest-margin-bodes-well-future\" target=\"_blank\">have a long position in its baby bonds</a> which recently started to offer the bondholders</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2185938635/image_2185938635.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747014-first-internet-bancorp-floating-debt-securities-offer-high-single-digit-yield", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 18:30:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747481", "title": "Tesla: Major Q4 Delivery Disappointment", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689016078/image_1689016078.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Israeli Prime Minister Netanyahu Meets With Elon Musk At Tesla In Fremont, CA\" data-id=\"1689016078\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"914px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689016078/image_1689016078.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689016078/image_1689016078.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689016078/image_1689016078.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689016078/image_1689016078.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689016078/image_1689016078.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689016078/image_1689016078.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689016078/image_1689016078.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689016078/image_1689016078.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Justin Sullivan/Getty Images News</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Over the last couple of months, one of the biggest winners in the market has been <b>Tesla, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TSLA\" title=\"Tesla, Inc.\">TSLA</a></span>). The electric vehicle (\u201cEV\u201d) maker has seen its shares soar after former President Donald Trump was</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1689016078/image_1689016078.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747481-tesla-major-q4-delivery-disappointment", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 18:24:01", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747494", "title": "January 2025 Perspective", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Conceptual image of man using smartphone to view bar graph\" data-id=\"1359134494\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1138px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">We Are</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><span>What\u2019s New</span></h2> <p>The holidays were far less happy for financial markets than the first 11 months of the year had been.</p> <p>We came into the month with yields on the rise, and this continued into the inflation print</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1359134494/image_1359134494.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747494-january-2025-perspective", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 18:10:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747490", "title": "Total Return Forecasts: Major Asset Classes - January 3, 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1752905583/image_1752905583.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Abstract trading chart with big data and infographics. 3D Fintech concept background with glowing candle chart\" data-id=\"1752905583\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1752905583/image_1752905583.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1752905583/image_1752905583.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1752905583/image_1752905583.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1752905583/image_1752905583.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1752905583/image_1752905583.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1752905583/image_1752905583.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1752905583/image_1752905583.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1752905583/image_1752905583.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">da-kuk</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The expected return over the long run for the Global Market Index (GMI) held steady in December vs. the <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741817-total-return-forecasts-major-asset-classes-december-3-2024\" rel=\"noopener\">previous month</a>. The unchanged forecast, based on three models defined below, reflects a second month with the highest return outlook in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1752905583/image_1752905583.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747490-total-return-forecasts-major-asset-classes-january-3-2025", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 18:02:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747482", "title": "Palo Alto Networks: Don't Ignore The Warning Signs (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426100645/image_1426100645.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Palo Alto Networks\" data-id=\"1426100645\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426100645/image_1426100645.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426100645/image_1426100645.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426100645/image_1426100645.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426100645/image_1426100645.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426100645/image_1426100645.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426100645/image_1426100645.jpg